title: #92Noon! Montage/Bercich/Twins/RonJohnson/Fleck
description: Tough montage to start, following the Vikings loss at Soldier field yesterday. Calls and Pete Bercich wrap up the first hour. Twins positivity midway through, getting ready for the ALDS matchup with the Yanks. Final hour has Ron Johnson in studio on Vikings & Gopher Football, followed by coach PJ Fleck's weekly appearance!
